      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON. ID. c., Feb. 90\nToday's session of the Binger Her\nmann trial was occupied In reading\nletters TO the jury written by Her\nmann to certain correspondents In\nOregon when he was commissioner\nOf the general land office. They\nwere identified by his former pri-\nvate secretary, Harry r. Rogers."
